# 🎯 Tic Tac Toe - Simple Web Game

A lightweight, browser-based **Tic Tac Toe** game built with just **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. This fun project is perfect for learning basic web development and JavaScript logic.
---

## 🔥 Live Demo

👉 [Click here to play online](#) *(Add your GitHub Pages/Netlify link once deployed)*

---

## 🕹️ Features

- 🎮 Two-player mode (X vs O)
- 🧠 Smart game logic with win/draw detection
- 🔄 Restart button to play again anytime
- 📱 Responsive design – play on mobile or desktop
- 💻 No frameworks – just pure, clean HTML/CSS/JavaScript

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

| Layer       | Technology |
|-------------|------------|
| Structure   | HTML5      |
| Styling     | CSS3       |
| Behavior    | JavaScript |

---

## 📂 Folder Structure

tic-tac-toe/ 
├── index.html # Main HTML file 
├── style.css # Game styles 
├── script.js # Game logic 
└── README.md # This documentation

